OL,5, Olwen Collier was in the Stag and      
OL,6, Pheasant in Carmel, south Wales, to    
OL,7, decorate a function room for her       
OL,8, daughter's 50th birthday party.        
OL,10,FBut when she was looking for it, dim   
OL,11,Flighting, poor signage and unclear     
OL,12,Fdirections meant she opened the wrong  
OL,13,Fdoor and fell into the cellar.         
OL,15,FShe suffered a fractured skull and died
OL,16,Ffrom her injuries in January 2023.     
OL,18,FNow her daughter is calling for tougher
OL,19,Fregulations after the landlords were   
OL,20,Fspared jail and kept their licence.    
